              "correct_example": "$\\int_{10}^{70} v(t)\\, dt$ is the distance, in feet, traveled by rocket A from $t = 10$ seconds to $t = 70$ seconds."
            }
          ],
          "common_traps": [
            "Saying 'change in velocity' (that would be $v(70) - v(10)$)"
